reviewText: The Plot Summary above says this DVD includes "Fractured Fairy Tales", "Peabody's Improbable History", the "Adventures of Dudley Doright", and "Aesop and Son".  It doesn't.  It does contain 16 Rocky and Bullwinkle chapters, which would be well worth the price, except that 12 of the 16 chapters are already available on the Complete Season DVDs.  So, the only new material you get is the four chapters of "The Guns of Abalone".  For die hard fans only.
